des:
Listen to an adventure-themed story with sound effects and prompts. Get ready for laughs and giggles. In this episode, skirt factor, Gizmo girl differs in formal clothing, preferring unisex clothing and a synergistic relationship between the sexes, as she moves to an innovation centered outlook, a design philosophy, moving away from sexist thinking to utilitarian and functionalism. Are you a part of this neo-theism?
